channel.description:
[img]http://www.titangame.net/images/titan.gif[/img]
[b]- Links -[/b] Website: [url=http://titangame.net]http://titangame.net[/url] Forums: [url=http://titangame.net/forums]http://titangame.net/forums[/url] Download: [url=http://titangame.net/play/client.jar]http://titangame.net/play/client.jar[/url]
Titan is cram packed with unique content with new content coming into the game every week. Some examples of new content coming soon are drygore weaponry dropped by the kalphite king and new capes for players achieving 200m xp in a skill.
[b]- Content -[/b]
[b]- Bosses -[/b] All GWD bosses Nex with full working stages Pest queen Blink Nomad Demon kings Tormented Demons

Glacors Chaos Tunnels Ice Stryeworms 24 working skills including Dungeoneering, Farming and Construction Jadinkos Above ground barrows Fight kiln with full rounds Fight caves with full rounds
